=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83e\\udd63<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> Caramel (pour servir)<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li>\\n        <\\/ul>\\n        <div style=\\\"height: 10px; background: #f1f2f6; margin: 20px -35px; border-top: 1px solid #dfe6e9; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfe6e9;\\\"><\\/div>\\n        <h3 style=\\\"margin: 25px 0; font-size: 1.5em; color: #2d3436; border-bottom: 2px solid #ffde59; padding-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block;\\\">\\ud83d\\udc68\\u200d\\ud83c\\udf73 Pr\\u00e9paration<\\/h3>\\n        <ol id=\\\"mpprecipe-instructions-list\\\" style=\\\"padding-left: 25px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.8; color: #2d3436;\\\">\\n            <li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Pr\\u00e9paration de la garniture aux pommes :** Dans un grand bol, m\\u00e9langez les pommes pel\\u00e9es et coup\\u00e9es en d\\u00e9s, le sucre roux, la cannelle, le quatre-\\u00e9pices, le sel et la farine tout usage. Ajoutez le jus de citron. Laissez reposer \\u00e0 temp\\u00e9rature ambiante pendant 15 minutes.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Pr\\u00e9paration du crumble :** Dans un autre grand bol, m\\u00e9langez les flocons d'avoine rapides, le sucre roux, la farine et le sel. Une fois bien combin\\u00e9, ajoutez lentement le beurre fondu en m\\u00e9langeant bien pour qu'il soit uniform\\u00e9ment r\\u00e9parti dans le crumble.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Assemblage :** Remplissez des ramequins aux trois quarts avec la garniture aux pommes. D\\u00e9posez 2 \\u00e0 3 cuill\\u00e8res \\u00e0 soupe de crumble sur le dessus et pressez l\\u00e9g\\u00e8rement.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Cuisson :** Pr\\u00e9chauffez le four \\u00e0 175\\u00b0C (350\\u00b0F). Enfournez les ramequins sur la grille du milieu pendant 25 \\u00e0 30 minutes.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Service :** Une fois cuit, laissez refroidir pendant 5 minutes avant de servir. Accompagnez de glace \\u00e0 la vanille et de caramel.<\\/li>\\n        <\\/ol>\\n    <\\/div>\\n    <div style=\\\"margin: 50px 0; border-top: 2px dashed #dfe6e9; padding-top: 40px; text-align: center;\\\">\\n        <h3 style=\\\"color: #2d3436; font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 30px;\\\">\\ud83d\\udd25 Cuisine en vid\\u00e9o !<\\/h3>\\n        \\n<div style=\\\"margin: 20px auto; max-width: 325px; min-width: 325px;\\\">\\n    <blockquote class=\\\"tiktok-embed\\\" cite=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/v\\/7420474770711383302\\\" data-video-id=\\\"7420474770711383302\\\" style=\\\"max-width: 605px;min-width: 325px;\\\">\\n        <section>\\n            <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"@tiktok\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/v\\/7420474770711383302\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Regarder la vid\\u00e9o sur TikTok<\\/a>\\n        <\\/section>\\n    <\\/blockquote>\\n    <script async src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/embed.js\\\"><\\/script>\\n<\\/div>\\n    <\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\",\"post_title\":\"Crumble aux pommes, caramel et glace vanille\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"trash\",\"comment_status\":\"open\",\"ping_status\":\"open\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"crumble-aux-pommes-caramel-et-glace-vanille__trashed\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2026-04-07 10:13:19\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2026-04-07 08:13:19\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"http:\\/\\/109.221.250.122\\/wordpress\\/?p=4844\",\"menu_order\":0,\"post_type\":\"post\",\"post_mime_type\":\"\",\"comment_count\":\"0\",\"filter\":\"raw\"},\"post_meta\":{\"_thumbnail_id\":[\"4843\"],\"_wp_trash_met