e=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf4b<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> 1\\/2 jus de citron<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83e\\udd63<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> 1 tasse de flocons d'avoine rapides<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf6f<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> 1 tasse de sucre roux (pour le crumble)<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf3e<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> 1 tasse de farine (pour le crumble)<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83e\\uddc8<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> 1\\/2 tasse de beurre non sal\\u00e9, fondu<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83e\\uddc2<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> 1 cuill\\u00e8re \\u00e0 caf\\u00e9 de sel (pour le crumble)<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf66<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> Glace \\u00e0 la vanille (pour servir)<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83e\\udd63<\\/span>\\n            <span><strong><\\/strong> Caramel (pour servir)<\\/span>\\n        <\\/li>\\n        <\\/ul>\\n        <div style=\\\"height: 10px; background: #f1f2f6; margin: 20px -35px; border-top: 1px solid #dfe6e9; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfe6e9;\\\"><\\/div>\\n        <h3 style=\\\"margin: 25px 0; font-size: 1.5em; color: #2d3436; border-bottom: 2px solid #ffde59; padding-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block;\\\">\\ud83d\\udc68\\u200d\\ud83c\\udf73 Pr\\u00e9paration<\\/h3>\\n        <ol id=\\\"mpprecipe-instructions-list\\\" style=\\\"padding-left: 25px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.8; color: #2d3436;\\\">\\n            <li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Pr\\u00e9paration de la garniture aux pommes :** Dans un grand bol, m\\u00e9langez les pommes Honeycrisp pel\\u00e9es et coup\\u00e9es en d\\u00e9s, 1\\/2 tasse de sucre roux, la cannelle, le piment de la Jama\\u00efque, 1 cuill\\u00e8re \\u00e0 caf\\u00e9 de sel, la farine tout usage et le jus de citron. Laissez reposer \\u00e0 temp\\u00e9rature ambiante pendant 15 minutes.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Pr\\u00e9paration du crumble :** Dans un autre grand bol, m\\u00e9langez les flocons d'avoine rapides, 1 tasse de sucre roux, 1 tasse de farine et 1 cuill\\u00e8re \\u00e0 caf\\u00e9 de sel. Une fois bien combin\\u00e9, ajoutez lentement le beurre fondu en m\\u00e9langeant bien pour qu'il soit uniform\\u00e9ment r\\u00e9parti dans le crumble.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Assemblage :** Remplissez vos ramequins aux trois quarts avec la garniture aux pommes. D\\u00e9posez 2 \\u00e0 3 cuill\\u00e8res \\u00e0 soupe de crumble sur le dessus et pressez l\\u00e9g\\u00e8rement.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Cuisson :** Pr\\u00e9chauffez le four \\u00e0 175\\u00b0C (350\\u00b0F). Enfournez les ramequins sur la grille du milieu pendant 25 \\u00e0 30 minutes.<\\/li><li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">**Service :** Une fois cuits, laissez refroidir pendant 5 minutes avant de servir. Accompagnez de glace \\u00e0 la vanille et de caramel.<\\/li>\\n        <\\/ol>\\n    <\\/div>\\n    <div style=\\\"margin: 50px 0; border-top: 2px dashed #dfe6e9; padding-top: 40px; text-align: center;\\\">\\n        <h3 style=\\\"color: #2d3436; font-size: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 30px;\\\">\\ud83d\\udd25 Cuisine en vid\\u00e9o !<\\/h3>\\n        \\n<div style=\\\"margin: 20px auto; max-width: 325px; min-width: 325px;\\\">\\n    <blockquote class=\\\"tiktok-embed\\\" cite=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/v\\/7420474770711383302\\\" data-video-id=\\\"7420474770711383302\\\" style=\\\"max-width: 605px;min-width: 325px;\\\">\\n        <section>\\n            <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"@tiktok\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/v\\/7420474770711383302\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Regarder la vid\\u00e9o sur TikTok<\\/a>\\n        <\\/section>\\n    <\\/blockquote>\\n    <script async src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tiktok.com\\/embed.js\\\"><\\/script>\\n<\\/div>\\n    <\\/div>\\n<\\/div>\",\"post_title\":\"Crumble aux pommes et caramel avec glace \\u00e0 la vanille\",\"post_excerpt\":\"\",\"post_status\":\"trash\",\"comment_status\":\"open\",\"ping_status\":\"open\",\"post_password\":\"\",\"post_name\":\"crumble-aux-pommes-et-caramel-avec-glace-a-la-vanille-2__trashed\",\"to_ping\":\"\",\"pinged\":\"\",\"post_modified\":\"2026-04-07 10:13:23\",\"post_modified_gmt\":\"2026-04-07 08:13:23\",\"post_content_filtered\":\"\",\"post_parent\":0,\"guid\":\"http:\\/\\/109.221.250.122\\/wordpress\\/?p=4